                                        "Models for mass burnt fraction",
                                        "UNIT IV SI ENGINE SIMULATION WITH GAS EXCHANGE PROCESS Introduction, gas exchange process, Heat transfer process, friction calculations, compression of simulated values, validation of the computer code, engine performance simulation, pressure crank angle diagram, brake power, brake thermal efficiency, effect of speed on performance"
