                                        "Parabolic and Hyperbolic equations. UNIT II FINITE DIFFERENCE AND FINITE VOLUME METHODS FOR DIFFUSION Derivation of finite difference equations– General Methods for first and second order accuracy – Finite volume formulation for steady and transient diffusion problems –Example problems– Use of Finite Difference and Finite Volume methods 200"
