                                        "UNIT V UNDECIDABILITY Unsolvable Problems and Computable Functions –PCP-MPCP- Recursive and recursively enumerable languages – Properties - Universal Turing machine -Tractable and Intractable problems  - P and NP completeness – Kruskal’s algorithm – Travelling Salesman Problem- -CNF SAT problems"
