                                "desc": "Steady state models giving rise to differential algebraic equation (DAE) systems; Rate basedApproaches for staged processes; Modeling of differential contactors – distributed parameter models of packed beds; Packed bed reactors; Modeling of reactive separation processes; Review of solution strategies for Differential Algebraic Equations (DAEs), Partial"
