                                "desc": "Simple examples of process models; Models giving rise to nonlinear algebraic equation (NAE) systems, -steady state models of flash vessels, equilibrium staged processes distillation columns, absorbers,strippers, CSTR, heat exchangers, etc.; Review of solution procedures and available numerical softwarelibraries"
