                                        "Theory of simple bending– Bending stress distribution – Flitched beams – Shear stress distribution",
                                        "UNIT III TORSION Torsion formulation stresses and deformation in circular and hollows shafts – Stepped shafts – Deflection in shafts fixed at the both ends – Stresses in helical springs – Deflection of helical springs, – Closed and Open Coiled helical springs – springs in series and parallel, carriage springs"
